    ConstrainedMOEADws

    public class MOEADws
extends MOEAD
    MOEA/D strategy with the Weigthed Sum approach. This class implements a weighted sum of the objective values as fitness assignment technique.

    Paper: Q. Zhang and H. Li, “MOEA/D: A Multiobjective Evolutionary Algorithm Based on Decomposition”, IEEE Transactions on Evolutionary Computation, vol. 11, no. 6, pp. 712–731, 2007.

    HISTORY:

    • (AR|JRR|SV, 1.0, March 2018) First release.

    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Aurora Ramirez (AR), Jose Raul Romero (JRR), Sebastian Ventura (SV)

    Knowledge Discovery and Intelligent Systems (KDIS) Research Group: http://www.uco.es/grupos/kdis
